spec_data.Name: ghc-hxt-charproperties
spec_data.Description:
Character properties defined by XML and Unicode standards. These modules
contain predicates for Unicode blocks and char properties and character
predicates defined by XML. Supported Unicode version is 7.0.0.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 16 Sep 2017 12:09:21 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Character properties and classes for XML and Unicode
